{"tid":788902,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"要報駕院都咪撚報智專","createTime":"2018-08-22T00:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T06:28:24.000Z","uid":46640,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6845f99cc8f5b3b57e95a9ea0dbfea40806d5029","tid":788902,"uid":46640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:11:12.000Z","msg":"報左智專plan，初頭聲稱有一位師傅負責幫你上堂，到上第一堂條友先話自己係導師組長，唔係主力教車，可能下堂唔係他教，然後每次上堂他真係揾唔同師傅同你上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n次撚次唔同師傅後果就係大家唔知對方做緊乜。今次A師傅話你冇問題，下次B師傅話你推拉軚都唔識，點會有人咁快放你出街揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到C師傅就好驚訝點解仲未有人教我掉頭泊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每一次上堂都好似重頭黎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打上去hotline第一次問，條友居然答我智專同非智專分別就只係有人幫你book 同自己book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母，原來所謂智專俾貴成千蚊只係有個真人幫你book堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n到我第二次打去發脾氣咁問，條友先話幫你反映番。呢個時候個導師組長先撲出黎話見你上堂時間唔定，他啲導師又係輪更，所以先會每次上堂唔同師傅。家下他先試下揾某個固定師傅時間睇下我夾唔夾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆你個街，你唔撚一早同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扼鳩左我八堂 ，仲要我打上去罵先同我講</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要報駕院都咪撚被人扼去報智專<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"ae420f5c77c43c2b414bc3843608dafe0b0282ce","tid":788902,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:13:17.000Z","msg":"駕院<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8acb7839c758a4fa8da40abe50dd4c772000bb0","tid":788902,"uid":12991,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:15:33.000Z","msg":"我之前智尊係同一個師傅教喎"},{"pid":"d1be436b3478c7ce82ee423a1632f821d2862bd9","tid":788902,"uid":46640,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"d8acb7839c758a4fa8da40abe50dd4c772000bb0","tid":788902,"uid":12991,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:15:33.000Z","msg":"我之前智尊係同一個師傅教喎"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:22:10.000Z","msg":"駕院條友同我講智專同非智專分別就只係有人幫你book 同自己book<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce885a35a1543d90ffd7c6f6ba37bedea61b307d","tid":788902,"uid":80719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:22:52.000Z","msg":"我而家學緊都係同一個師傅教wo"},{"pid":"c3130eaa777a2afc6d8973f195269e571e3faaba","tid":788902,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T01:13:02.000Z","msg":"你邊間駕院呀 觀駕呀？"},{"pid":"56bb0ce54f73c5d9f2bb5bb3955481a96ad49696","tid":788902,"uid":188311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1be436b3478c7ce82ee423a1632f821d2862bd9","tid":788902,"uid":46640,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"d8acb7839c758a4fa8da40abe50dd4c772000bb0","tid":788902,"uid":12991,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:15:33.000Z","msg":"我之前智尊係同一個師傅教喎"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:22:10.000Z","msg":"駕院條友同我講智專同非智專分別就只係有人幫你book 同自己book<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T01:14:32.000Z","msg":"同我以前學差咁遠既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9f2cf7d2d55e5dc7cd0c86a35db194bfe5e61b","tid":788902,"uid":24021,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T01:18:15.000Z","msg":"智尊係一個師傅同車跟到尾wo 點會係只係幫你book"},{"pid":"9881b4d62e0790a5d08f17e01f7f4942dcd4fbe3","tid":788902,"uid":50076,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T01:20:09.000Z","msg":"屌7佢啦<br />\n<br />\n係同師傅架"},{"pid":"cac3fdd9b3d436e40b1bee6d97dee157